This paper is likely to belong to the cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) sub-category as it deals with the development of routing strategies in power line networks. It could also belong to the cs.SY (Systems and Control) sub-category as it involves the estimation of the network topology. The paper also involves the use of communication modems, which could place it in the cs.IT (Information Theory) sub-category. Additionally, the paper deals with the distribution network, which could place it in the cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science) sub-category. Finally, the paper could also belong to the cs.MM (Multimedia) sub-category as it involves the measurement of network admittance.
